This R package contains Rust code which depends on the Rust crates listed below.
The source code is vendored in the R package and can also be found at
https://crates.io/crates/XXXX, where XXXX is a crate name.
The authors of these Rust crates are listed below.

Aleksey Kladov <aleksey.kladov@gmail.com>   : id-arena
Alex Crichton <alex@alexcrichton.com>       : cfg-if, proc-macro2, wit-bindgen, wit-bindgen-core, wit-bindgen-rust, wit-bindgen-rust-macro, wit-parser
Amanieu d'Antras <amanieu@gmail.com>        : hashbrown
Andrew Gallant <jamslam@gmail.com>          : memchr
bluss                                       : either, matrixmultiply, memchr, rawpointer
Brendan Zabarauskas <bjzaba@yahoo.com.au>   : approx
Bryant Luk <code@bryantluk.com>             : leb128fmt
David B. Dahl <dahl@stat.byu.edu>           : dahl-bellnumber, dahl-partition, dahl-salso, rbindings, roxido, roxido_macro
David Tolnay <dtolnay@gmail.com>            : anyhow, itoa, prettyplease, proc-macro2, quote, semver, serde, serde_core, serde_derive, serde_json, syn, unicode-ident, zmij
Erick Tryzelaar <erick.tryzelaar@gmail.com> : serde, serde_core, serde_derive, serde_json, unicode-xid
